text: Héricourt may refer to: * Héricourt, Pas-de-Calais, a commune of the Pas-de- Calais department in France * Héricourt, Haute-Saône, a commune of the Haute- Saône department in France == Other == * Héricourt-en-Caux, a commune of the Seine-Maritime department in France * Héricourt-sur-Thérain, a commune of the Oise department in France * Battle of Héricourt, 1474, part of the Burgundian Wars
title: Héricourt
